        HIDE BROWSE {&BROWSE-NAME}.
        HIDE FRAME {&FRAME-NAME}.
        IF {&WINDOW-NAME}:HEIGHT LT 28.57 THEN
        {&WINDOW-NAME}:HEIGHT = 28.57.
