                                               - BROWSE {&BROWSE-NAME}:ROW + 1
            BROWSE {&BROWSE-NAME}:WIDTH        = FRAME {&FRAME-NAME}:WIDTH
            .
        VIEW FRAME {&FRAME-NAME}.
        VIEW BROWSE {&BROWSE-NAME}.
    END. /* do with */
